    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cardalaxy is a <strong>card upgrading</strong> game with <strong>4X inspiration</strong> and <br><strong><i>5+ different victories</i></strong><i>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Planets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your planets with buildings to increase their value. Advance through multiple tiers of buildings, each with better effects and bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/21302355d7d81d1b9649b05c151b09ae.poster.avif?t=1742348406\" width=364 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/21302355d7d81d1b9649b05c151b09ae.webm?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/21302355d7d81d1b9649b05c151b09ae.mp4?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Research, Explore, Develop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect points and use them in each of the different systems to advance your empire. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/200b453be81b3ee91039d85e3eaa4ec2.poster.avif?t=1742348406\" width=350 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/200b453be81b3ee91039d85e3eaa4ec2.webm?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/200b453be81b3ee91039d85e3eaa4ec2.mp4?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend your Empire</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies are constantly threatening the empire. Collect defense and use it to fight them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/80decc2e7c218112f07267a931081892.poster.avif?t=1742348406\" width=610 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/80decc2e7c218112f07267a931081892.webm?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/80decc2e7c218112f07267a931081892.mp4?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achieve Victory!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path to victory - Production, Defense, Wellness, Science, or Exploration. Each has a unique way to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/bc5cc8bef5ed5b262d9b2385238f8b47.poster.avif?t=1742348406\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/bc5cc8bef5ed5b262d9b2385238f8b47.webm?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314690/extras/bc5cc8bef5ed5b262d9b2385238f8b47.mp4?t=1742348406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
